description.narrative:
The adviser will be part of UNDP's democratic governance team and to this extent work in close collaboration with inclusive development, the recovery and peace building programme and other units. The work funktion will contribute to parts of the UNDP's country-programme, in particular within the thematic areas of democracy, good governance, human rights, conflict, youth, social security e tal.
In addition, the adviser will be responsible for adivising the Democratic Governance Team on planning, implementation, political inoovation and program and capacity building.
